title: NFL Week 6 Fantasy, DFS, Gambling Picks with Heath Cummings, Stephen Oh (Football 10/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sr. Fantasy Analyst Heath Cummings to break down Week 6 from a fantasy perspective and figure out who to start, who to sit, who to buy low on and who are the best DFS plays. Can you trust Jameis Winston for the rest of the season? Find out here. Then Stephen Oh of SportsLine drops by to dig into the data and break down Week 6 from a gambling and fantasy analytical perspective.
